// UI style configuration for Vampire Survivors.
// Edit while the game is running — changes are applied instantly (hot-reload).
//
// Parameters:
// - bg_color:    Background color for full-screen overlays (title, game-over, etc.) (RGB, 0.0–1.0)
// - title_color: Color of the "Vampire Survivors" heading on the title screen (RGB, 0.0–1.0)
//
// Design palette reference (docs/04_ui_ux.md):
//   Background:       #1a0a2e  → (r: 0.102, g: 0.039, b: 0.180)
//   Text emphasized:  #ffd700  → (r: 1.000, g: 0.843, b: 0.000)
//
// Button colors/dimensions → config/ui/hud/menu_button.ron
// Heading font size        → config/ui/hud/screen_heading.ron
// Upgrade card styles      → config/ui/hud/upgrade_card.ron
UiStyleConfig(
    bg_color:    (r: 0.102, g: 0.039, b: 0.180),
    title_color: (r: 1.000, g: 0.843, b: 0.000),
)
